---
title: Smart Mexican-Inspired Double Shrimp Skillet with Guacamole
description: Tonight's skillet dinner is packed with Mexican-style spices, fresh cilantro and creamy guacamole! A pepper and zucchini hash rounds it out for a delicious, light meal.

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
